                        <cell cols="1" role="data" rows="1"><p>slain in the (13</p><p>troubles after
                            the death of</p><p>Judas.</p></cell>
                        <cell cols="1" role="data" rows="1"><p>15). (160). (163-2).
                            (143).</p></cell>
                    </row>
                    <row cols="1" role="data" rows="1">
